data.description: Gorgeous home in great neighborhood with private park. 4 bedroom. 2 full bath, separate tub and shower in master as well as dual sinks. Wood look tile floors in common areas, with carpet in bedrooms. Large open feel in living space. Indoor laundry with shelves and cabinets. Plantation Shutters throughout. Covered back patio. Concrete pad in back behind RV gates for parking with hook-ups(50 am service and dump). Shed for extra storage space. Peach, Pear, Apricot, Plum Trees in fully landscaped front and back yard. Gas Fire pit in back yard.  This home is being advertised with RV hook ups including water, electric, and sewer connections. Not all RVs or campers are compatible with the electric plug that is installed. Buyer to verify this during the inspection period time frame.  Cameras on premises, voice and audio recording may be in use. Back patio furniture and outdoor furniture are negotiable with right offer  **Seller is willing to pay up to 3% to buy down Buyers interest rate. **
